 Davido’s Uncle,  Osun 2018 PDP gubernatorial candidate, Senator Ademola Adeleke has graduated with a Bachelors Degree in Criminal Justice in Atlanta Metropolitan State College, US. His convocation was attended by his brother, Adedeji Adeleke, his son BRed, and other family members. A good friend of Senator Ademola Adeleke, Dele Momodou took to his twitter page to congratulate him on the degree. He wrote: Special congratulations to my main man SENATOR ADEMOLA NURUDEEN ADELEKE on this great determination and achievement. There’s always a way where there’s a WILL to succeed…